    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在ServiceMesh后面加了一个判断节点D，指向HelmChart。如果判断为是，就走K8sCluster这条线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
